{"nodes":[{"nodeID":"2583","text":"Therefore the God of the Bible does not exist","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:26:22"},{"nodeID":"2584","text":"The Bible teaches no such thing","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:26:22"},{"nodeID":"2585","text":"I challenge Dr. Curley to read me a single passage of Scripture that teaches that infants are damned because of original sin","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:26:22"},{"nodeID":"2586","text":"Infants are damned because of original sin.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:26:22"},{"nodeID":"2587","text":"The Bible teaches original sin.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:26:22"},{"nodeID":"2588","text":"It is contradictory that a perfectly good entity allows children to be damned","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:26:22"},{"nodeID":"2589","text":"On the contrary Jesus took up the little children in his arms and blessed them saying  Let the little children come to me... for such is the kingdom of heaven","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:26:22"},{"nodeID":"2590","text":"If the Bible teaches the contrary the claim is not true","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:26:22"},{"nodeID":"2591","text":"CA","type":"CA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:26:22"},{"nodeID":"2592","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:26:23","scheme":"Ignorance","schemeID":"19"},{"nodeID":"2593","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:26:23"},{"nodeID":"2594","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:26:23"}],"edges":[{"edgeID":"2489","fromID":"2584","toID":"2591","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"2490","fromID":"2591","toID":"2586","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"2491","fromID":"2585","toID":"2592","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"2492","fromID":"2592","toID":"2584","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"2493","fromID":"2586","toID":"2593","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"2494","fromID":"2587","toID":"2593","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"2495","fromID":"2588","toID":"2593","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"2496","fromID":"2593","toID":"2583","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"2497","fromID":"2589","toID":"2594","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"2498","fromID":"2590","toID":"2594","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"2499","fromID":"2594","toID":"2584","formEdgeID":null}],"locutions":[]}